The paper proposes a model for sentiment classification and topic extraction from users' reviews. This falls under the domain of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning, which are covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it covers NLP and sentiment analysis. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new model for classification. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possibility as the paper deals with topic extraction. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) are less likely but still possible as they cover machine learning and NLP-related topics.
